{"tid":2418892,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：港人須接受及知道香港是共產黨揸旗 愛國定愛黨是鳩旦啦","createTime":"2021-02-23T03:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-23T12:39:41.000Z","uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"44fdd354a22db8ff9c9a5f421f9290654ddfe3f2","tid":2418892,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:14:32.000Z","msg":"聶德權：港人須接受及知道國家執政黨是共產黨<br />\n<br />\n公務員事務局長聶德權在本台節目表示，港澳辦主任夏寶龍有關「愛國者治港」的講話，是重申特首、行政會議成員、立法會議員、非政權性的區域組織，以及公務人員等政治體制內的人員，本身都要是愛國者，最基本的要求是，要擁護《基本法》及效忠特區。<br />\n<br />\n聶德權說，香港法律和公務員制度等，雖然與內地不同，但香港作為國家治理體制的一部份，必須清晰接受及知道國家執政黨是共產黨。被問到是否一直都愛黨，聶德權就指，自己一直很清楚國家的政治體制、特區的憲制地位，以及回歸後的憲制秩序。<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380150\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2Fnews%2Flocal%2F2380150&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=50f83f21\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/news/local/2380150</a>"},{"pid":"cc70631ab0f81d19310c0bdd490e160981a8392e","tid":2418892,"uid":366655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">被問到是否一直都愛黨</span></span>，聶德權就指，自己一直很清楚國家的政治體制、特區的憲制地位，以及回歸後的憲制秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bbad8055ec7e25bfcbbb22186fe229e02cfd2300","tid":2418892,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc70631ab0f81d19310c0bdd490e160981a8392e","tid":2418892,"uid":366655,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:30:48.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><span class=\"red\">被問到是否一直都愛黨</span></span>，聶德權就指，自己一直很清楚國家的政治體制、特區的憲制地位，以及回歸後的憲制秩序。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:33:11.000Z","msg":"清楚體制可以係知道有好多問題，唔等於愛喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cfb3fe4f5b992655e4c43342456a092b3db79dcb","tid":2418892,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:34:29.000Z","msg":"講到明"},{"pid":"3d88a532889bbe4f379e0d83713370f2649fc6b6","tid":2418892,"uid":389615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cfb3fe4f5b992655e4c43342456a092b3db79dcb","tid":2418892,"uid":76063,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T03:34:29.000Z","msg":"講到明"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-23T12:39:41.000Z","msg":"咁林鄭愛唔愛黨？<br />\n<br />\n共產黨係一個堅定的無神論政黨。信奉馬克思唯物主義及科學無神論。不接受有神論及唯心論。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭信奉天主教，不真心愛黨。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/1655732/%E5%85%B1%E9%9D%92%E5%9C%98%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%B0%E8%80%85%20%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%85%A5%E9%BB%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F1655732%2F%25E5%2585%25B1%25E9%259D%2592%25E5%259C%2598%25E5%25BE%25AE%25E5%258D%259A%25EF%25BC%259A%25E6%259C%2589%25E5%25AE%2597%25E6%2595%2599%25E4%25BF%25A1%25E4%25BB%25B0%25E8%2580%2585%2520%25E7%25B5%2595%25E4%25B8%258D%25E8%2583%25BD%25E5%2585%25A5%25E9%25BB%25A8&d=x6KcuROq%2Bx9sojjRb0T2XkVeFFKYYtZMgzuY3n553xQ%3D&h=46434369\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/1655732/%E5%85%B1%E9%9D%92%E5%9C%98%E5%BE%AE%E5%8D%9A%EF%BC%9A%E6%9C%89%E5%AE%97%E6%95%99%E4%BF%A1%E4%BB%B0%E8%80%85%20%E7%B5%95%E4%B8%8D%E8%83%BD%E5%85%A5%E9%BB%A8</a>"}]}